---
title: Quick White Fish & Creamy Parsley Sauce with Roasted Pumpkin & Green Bean Salad
description: Tender pan-seared fish never fails to satisfy! It has all the familiar tastes of home cooking at its finest, plus a creamy herb sauce and a side of easy roast potato and pumpkin which make up the perfect accompaniments to this tasty dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
